title: Jeff Frane pedals into the Wilde w/ new U.S.-made bike brand making Ti & Steel dream rides
content:
We’ve been watching closely on social media as Jeff Frane’s bicycle passion project evolved into a full-fledged bike brand. And with the announcement of Wilde Bicycle Company, that day is finally here.
